option.value:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?> <LinearLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" xmlns:app="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res-auto" android:layout_width="wrap_content" android:layout_height="wrap_content" android:orientation="vertical" android:padding="24dp" android:background="@drawable/rounded_bg" android:gravity="center_horizontal">
<TextView android:id="@+id/tv_stockfish_elo_title" android:layout_width="wrap_content" android:layout_height="wrap_content" android:text="Choose Stockfish elo" android:textAppearance="@style/TextAppearance.AppCompat.Large" android:textColor="@android:color/white" android:layout_marginBottom="12dp"/>
<TextView android:id="@+id/tv_stockfish_elo_value" android:layout_width="wrap_content" android:layout_height="wrap_content" android:layout_marginBottom="12dp" android:text="2537" android:textColor="@android:color/white" android:textAppearance="@style/TextAppearance.AppCompat.Medium" />
<SeekBar android:id="@+id/seekbar_stockfish_elo" android:layout_width="250dp" android:layout_height="wrap_content" android:min="1" android:max="30" android:progress="15" android:layout_marginBottom="20dp" app:progressTint="@color/primaryLight"/>
<Button android:id="@+id/btn_stockfish_elo_start" android:layout_width="120dp" android:layout_height="48dp" android:text="Start" android:textStyle="bold" android:elevation="2dp"/>
</LinearLayout>
